rrative reduces support by 57 points.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"leaf\": \"Supply_Chain_Resilience_Priority\",\n      \"score\": 554,\n      \"confidence\": 0.64,\n      \"reasoning\": \"Strong nationalism and cosmopolitan orientation create a dual concern for secure supply chains, but the financial narrative raises doubts about funding integrity, producing a 60-point drop.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"leaf\": \"Critical_Infrastructure_Public_Investment_Support\",\n      \"score\": 442,\n      \"confidence\": 0.66,\n      \"reasoning\": \"High trust in government and experts initially supports investment, yet the stablecoin-distrust campaign effectively targets concerns about funding sources given the person's low digital literacy and financial exclusion, driving a 56-point reduction.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}",
